  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/129256738-gili-levy">Gili Levy</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer9700825833279736562">AGREED 100% CHAOL DESERVES BETTER AND AELIN AND ROWAS IS SO FORCED.</span>

    <br/>

    <span class="xhrCommentFooter greyText">
      Feb 05, 2022 11:45AM
    </span>

    
